FBIS4-16399 "drsov073_f_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk: Odessa Incident `Over and Done With' Kravchuk: Odessa Incident `Over and Done With' LD1504082794 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 0700 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504082794 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] Ukrainian President Leonid Kravchuk stated on arrival in Moscow that the incident involving the Black Sea vessel and seamen in Odessa is over and done with. Kravchuk noted: As far as politicians are concerned, the main thing was to regard it precisely in this light. Moreover, the incident is not as big as it was made out to be. The Ukrainian president's view is that it is a signal to begin solving the Black Sea fleet's problems without delay.
